metadata.name: Ideological Conflict
metadata.description:
The ideological clash, a cacophony of screams  
Rising up from a vortex of discordant dreams  
A chorus of voices, so insistent and loud  
Locking horns in a deathly, eternal shroud  
Two sides in a battle of thought and opinion  
Both clinging to their beliefs with a firm conviction.
